instruction: Retrieve a list of cities in the United Kingdom with a population greater than 500,000.
output: The cities in the United Kingdom with a population greater than 500,000 are: London (8.9 million), Birmingham (1.18 million), Glasgow (621,000), Leeds (765,000), Sheffield (569,000), Liverpool (484,000), Manchester (552,000), Bristol (558,000), Leicester (536,000), Coventry (354,000), Bradford (527,000), and Newcastle upon Tyne (548,000).
